Package: lindasR
Type: Package
Title: Tools to Query the Swiss Federal Linked Data Service (LINDAS)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Zumbach", , "david.zumbach@gfzb.ch", c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides convenient access to the Swiss Federal Linked Data
    Service (LINDAS) via its 'SPARQL' endpoint (<https://ld.admin.ch/>).
    The package allows users to query datasets, perform full-text search
    across literals, and retrieve multilingual metadata with configurable
    language preferences.
URL: https://ld.admin.ch
BugReports: https://github.com/zumbov2/lindas/issues
